
<h3>About CiderBase</h3>

<div class="boxcontent">CiderBase is a website for managing germplasm and germplasm-related data for the Peck lab at Cornell University.</div>

<div class="boxcontent">Note that data on CiderBase are associated with Data Agreements and that they are not necessarily in the public domain. Please contact the authors of the data if you are interested in any aspect of data production or analysis.</div>
